{"tid":831153,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"（打手/非打手入）求Android機推薦","createTime":"2018-09-21T16:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T04:20:04.000Z","uid":66380,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e7302a902bc38281bcdadac7e5b774cd78a14342","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"用左Android 差唔多8年...每部Android都係用半年就好撚慢，一年左右就會打柴，有得換電都仲用到耐啲,一過保養壞電真係嬲。<br />\n用緊LG G6, 大半年，廣角鏡真係一流，但部機好易發熱，一熱/叉電throttling真係慢到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有諗過不如轉iPhone.. 因為朋友用2-3年都冇變慢問題。如果Android每年換... iPhone用到兩年其實都好似抵返。<br />\n但係點知今次iPhone 過萬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以都係打消念頭<br />\n而家有冇邊部android已出或者就推介？<br />\nLG 廣角真係好上癮，但係開相機好慢...易發熱真係想脫離LG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望影相好用（開相機快都好重要）"},{"pid":"fb59b62decf736240ccf127bd3d1a3547c78bd21","tid":831153,"uid":137694,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"Iphone se換左oneplus 6 5個月，除左喇叭差啲之外冇投訴，相機唔係最好，但都好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eaf1ca69996d97ddd0d78006a242ebd57419e3","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb59b62decf736240ccf127bd3d1a3547c78bd21","tid":831153,"uid":137694,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"Iphone se換左oneplus 6 5個月，除左喇叭差啲之外冇投訴，相機唔係最好，但都好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"巴打我想問IPhone換Android後用落有咩唔慣或者各有咩唔好？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb3fa064253d0adad39127ce5f30618be8215b1","tid":831153,"uid":109386,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:08:41.000Z","msg":"pocophone，鬼佬最愛，又平又正，壞左都唔心疼"},{"pid":"eda53afa457d36680a15acbbe1000902ebdc6d36","tid":831153,"uid":57021,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"唔用 NFC 就 pocophone f1，用就 oneplus 6 or mi 8"},{"pid":"f00321271fa2ec1e091527757365c3f4c128aed0","tid":831153,"uid":72186,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"提醒：oneplus 即係支那步步高"},{"pid":"2b6cc52f456cf9fb534b4f467654a7ba774e9f89","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f00321271fa2ec1e091527757365c3f4c128aed0","tid":831153,"uid":72186,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"提醒：oneplus 即係支那步步高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"而家愈出愈多支那機.... 但係Android入面其他廠又好唔爭氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc3c370727ee0563da3653ac7d96b5e59d85724","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865248a8ec164622ef6aeb99d0141e1572ecf130","tid":831153,"uid":34634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"用緊V20, 都係有類似問題<br />\n<br />\n之前有發熱問題，自從冇用玻璃貼之後就冇事了<br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係原生相機app，新買返黎嗰陣都幾快；用耐咗就撳極啲掣都冇反應咁<br />\n<br />\n結果用咗第三方相機app之後反應快好多, 但冇咗廣角<br />\n<br />\n依家真心唔知android有咩新機啱心水，有得換電嘅新機似乎已經好難搵到（冇電嗰陣即刻拆粒電出黎換真條方便過一路插住尿袋）"},{"pid":"a6c161dbabd91df153cf358deb1b5047953027fb","tid":831153,"uid":158145,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"Note 9"},{"pid":"8649da280a10f0542ed9c99f6fd3cadcd7fb4557","tid":831153,"uid":57504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"Pixel"},{"pid":"7324edae5ec3577446c84c3a4a4104ceb648b095","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"865248a8ec164622ef6aeb99d0141e1572ecf130","tid":831153,"uid":34634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"用緊V20, 都係有類似問題<br />\n<br />\n之前有發熱問題，自從冇用玻璃貼之後就冇事了<br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係原生相機app，新買返黎嗰陣都幾快；用耐咗就撳極啲掣都冇反應咁<br />\n<br />\n結果用咗第三方相機app之後反應快好多, 但冇咗廣角<br />\n<br />\n依家真心唔知android有咩新機啱心水，有得換電嘅新機似乎已經好難搵到（冇電嗰陣即刻拆粒電出黎換真條方便過一路插住尿袋）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:59:11.000Z","msg":"V20真心係用過最多最正既一部android。前後廣角。<br />\n然後可以換電。<br />\n熱而減慢既問題root左就解決，用tasker set佢45度先減慢cpu...<br />\n可惜我嗰部浸壞左先迫住換G6.."},{"pid":"790f5be4ec1ac0445c8d3b4799bb6ad41bf1bec8","tid":831153,"uid":207161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:01:20.000Z","msg":"用緊v30 覆你<br />\n真核電 聽歌正<br />\n不過相機質素真係好差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3e39844c2f1ec4d45d1c2ac0bec8d36c91c89d","tid":831153,"uid":190150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"廣角鏡一流+1 一去冇回頭<br />\n等緊v40睇下咩價位睇下v40+ or g7+ 6gb ram實夠用多3年起<br />\nLG依家粒電係合成鋰電 同其他鋰電唔同 睇好多utube review3000一叉都夠一日用<br />\n利申 用左g5兩年幾 除左電倒水(所以有兩粒電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 同小殘影開心使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633d49c953113ea1e4f5fe9fce7ae6a79c891f31","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a3e39844c2f1ec4d45d1c2ac0bec8d36c91c89d","tid":831153,"uid":190150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"廣角鏡一流+1 一去冇回頭<br />\n等緊v40睇下咩價位睇下v40+ or g7+ 6gb ram實夠用多3年起<br />\nLG依家粒電係合成鋰電 同其他鋰電唔同 睇好多utube review3000一叉都夠一日用<br />\n利申 用左g5兩年幾 除左電倒水(所以有兩粒電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 同小殘影開心使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"我係由G4開始用LG<br />\nG5,V20到而家用G6<br />\n廣角一用冇回頭...去旅行影相真係一流<br />\n加埋可以換電真心正。<br />\n所以V20真係好好。可惜LG已經唔出可以換電既機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果繼續出真係一定唔會轉會"},{"pid":"8afabe25712067b1ed5cdc2541c047effd4b2f09","tid":831153,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61eaf1ca69996d97ddd0d78006a242ebd57419e3","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb59b62decf736240ccf127bd3d1a3547c78bd21","tid":831153,"uid":137694,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"Iphone se換左oneplus 6 5個月，除左喇叭差啲之外冇投訴，相機唔係最好，但都好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"巴打我想問IPhone換Android後用落有咩唔慣或者各有咩唔好？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"最唔慣係冇airdrop, 相薄排位，wtsapp 冇得set某個grp嘅相唔save, 其他都冇咩唔慘"},{"pid":"bcb7ee2fa2288917d00127a1f3947c4b053fffbc","tid":831153,"uid":147376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"符合樓主要求<br />\n細機:pixel 2, 3(影相最靚) , s9, g7(有廣角，影相一般)，二手iphone x<br />\n<br />\n大機:note 9, s9+, u12+(倒水電同要適應粒制)"},{"pid":"d291c909a07c8fc3949ea9ed640e47a703e0bbc5","tid":831153,"uid":66380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757a776bbf670ecee894bedae91